			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Mostly hoping to see improvements on Discordant Melodies(and have it stay in), because it may increase spell agro 100%, but 100% on top of 0 is still 0 for the majority of songs(99% of song agro is can only be gained through proximity, and it doesn't &quot;build&quot; like most agro).  Even doubling song agro isn't going to make any real difference now.  The only way it would stack up is if we twisted DOTs, and their agro was already severely cut.
<br />

<br />
Also hoping shield of notes is changed.  It just doesn't fall into any &quot;useful&quot; catagories at the moment.  It doesn't last long enough to be considered any sort of weaker version of a &quot;defensive&quot; AA, nor is the re-use time fast enough.  
<br />

<br />
And it is simply not strong enough to be a &quot;Life-saver&quot; AA, 25% is never going to save me those times when I need it.  50% might, though things hit so hard nowadays it's iffy.
<br />

<br />
I might use it, rarely, on a tough pull, but a speed-boost would be far more useful for that sort of situtation.</span></td>
